NAME

    CGI::Session::ID::MD5_Base64 - CGI::Session ID driver based on Base64
    encoding

SYNOPSIS

        use CGI::Session;

        $session = new CGI::Session("id:MD5_Base64", undef, { Directory => '/tmp' };

DESCRIPTION

    CGI::Session::ID::MD5_Base64 is to generate MD5 digest Base64 encoded
    random ids. The library does not require any arguments.

